order_number.orig_str: शासन निर्णय क्रमांकः उपकें-२०२४/ प्र.क्र.२३३/ आरोग्य-४

para_trans: Funny way, Ta. Regarding sanction of new Health Sub-Centre at Paranda, Dist. Dharashiv.
Government Decision No: Sub-Collector-2024 / P.No.233 / Health-4

Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries) Mumbai: ASH / Rooms-7A / T-8 / Dharakampuri / Sub-Centre / Establishment / Dharashiv / 2243-45/24, dated 07.06.2024.
Introduction: - Mouje Dharkapimpri, Ta. Health facilities to the residents of the locality at Paranda, Dist. Dharashiv
A new health sub-centre needs to be sanctioned in line with the supply, so a health sub-centre is to be set up at the site.
Approval was under consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Funny way, Ta. This Government has sanctioned a new Health Sub-Centre at Paranda, District Dharashiv.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
